edu.uci.inf111.SelfCheckOut.Gui
Class Actions

java.lang.Object
  edu.uci.inf111.SelfCheckOut.Gui.Actions

public class Actions
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains the actions that can be called from the Graphical User Interface of the Self CheckOut System. It also includes an internal action to print the contents of the shopping cart
